Gollumix is a full 32 bit operating system running on i386 architecture.

Here the features supported:

- running in 32 protected mode;
- multitasking (support for task switch, scheduler an so on);
- simple phisical memory manager;
- AT keyboard (8242 controller) support;
- RS232 serial line support;
- a simplified TTY layer implemented (6 consoles: 4 locals and 2 serials);
- native boot and boot loader (lilo, grub) support;
- pic (8159 chip) support;
- 82077AA CHMOS Floppy Driver support;
- pit support;
